article.description: — Tymu Chenery's 31 points led Binghamton over Le Moyne 91-79 on Saturday.
article.headline: Chenery scores 31, Binghamton defeats Le Moyne 91-79
article.linkText: Chenery scores 31, Binghamton defeats Le Moyne 91-79
article.story: BINGHAMTON, N.Y. -- — Tymu Chenery's 31 points led Binghamton over Le Moyne 91-79 on Saturday. Chenery added 12 rebounds and four blocks for the Bearcats (6-4). Armon Harried scored 18 points while shooting 6 of 11 from the field and 5 for 6 from the line. Dan Petcash had 14 points and shot 4 for 7 from beyond the arc. Luke Sutherland led the way for the Dolphins (3-7) with 35 points and two blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
